title: Pete Ham (Badfinger): 7 Park Avenue - Japanese CD with Bonus Tra
description:
Great release of demos & never released songs that shows what a genius Pete Ham was
and how far he could have gone had he not taken himself away from us.

This version of the CD from Japan has bonus tracks #19-23.
